  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe consensus specs [instruct us to verify](https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/dev/specs/deneb/beacon-chain.md#modified-verify_and_notify_new_payload) the execution payload `block_hash` and `versioned_hashes` before sending `engine_newPayload` to the EE. This is because the EE could be syncing, putting us into optimistic sync mode. These checks only need to be performed during optimistic sync.\r\n\r\nWe already verify the `block_hash` and now we just need the `versioned_hashes` for `deneb`.\r\n",
